title: Pair of Mickelson brain farts sets U.S. back in Presidents Cup
text: Pair of Mickelson brain farts sets U.S. back in Presidents Cup Friday, 9 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) The International team wound up winning two holes in one at the Presidents Cup on Friday when Phil Mickelson didn't know the rules and won its first team session in four years to pull within one point of the United States
